io.github.iwyfewwnt.uwutils

Class UwSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.iwyfewwnt.uwutils.UwSystem

  • public final class UwSystem
extends Object
    A system utility.

    UwSystem is the utility class that provide functionality to operate with Java's System module.
